page.title: 01OVERVIEW
page.content: Milton Keynes has been built up over the past 10 years and it has one of the biggest shopping centres.Heelands is quite a new estate because it was built about 5 years ago.In Bradwell Village there are a lot of old houses. One of them is called The Moat House. Near the pub there are some houses that are quite new but they have been built to look old.Right at the bottom of Bradwell there is a railway that runs from London(Euston) to Glasgow.In Kiln Farm and Stacey Bushes there are lots of Warehouses and Factories. Loughton is very nice.It has 4 lakes. It also has some stables with about 20 horse.Most of the houses there are old but they are building a new estate onto it.In the southwest corner of our grid there are lots of farms.They are Two Mile Ash farm,Whitehouse farm and Common farm.
